{
  "stem": "17543.3",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I remember giving me a glass of milk, and I couldn't finish it because I felt I would be sick if I would finish it.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And they arranged it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Of course, there were several people like me, who wanted to go back to Hungary, thought maybe their parents is alive.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And you know, these women around me, they knew my mother wasn't alive.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "They didn't told me.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And-- otherwise, I wouldn't have gone back.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I wouldn't wanted to go back, because I heard from my father before the war we have relatives in America-- his cousins, who settled in America turn of the century.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "So if I would knew I don't find nobody, I wouldn't gone back.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So anyway are going back, and I was-- To Budapest.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Budapest.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, because they disappeared.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean, they wasn't nowhere.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And these ladies from the Red Cross, they's taken over that area for re-established people who are coming out of camps.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Maybe they came-- they was looking after people in the same place before we came, because was the last one who find.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] when I went back to Hungary, to Budapest, it was straight, really, into a hospital, because my skin was covered in spots and my tummy grown so big.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I was really-- I don't know how I was looking.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I was looking most likely awful.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, they-- they said this is the general-- not everybody had it such a bad way, but that's the average when people restart eating.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Then the system can't cope with it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they give me some cream and bandage on me all over, you know.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] they didn't give me anything for my tummy.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
